artist: Kristen Ross is a contemporary landscape painter based in Boulder, Colorado. She paints the places she loves to explore, celebrating the complexity of the West’s wild spaces with vivid color and intricate detail. Inspired by her love for the outdoors, Kristen’s acrylic paintings seek to capture the essence of time spent in nature through layers of vibrant color and expressive linework. Originally from Atlanta, Georgia, Ross holds a Bachelor of Fine Arts from the Rhode Island School of Design. Her work is exhibited in galleries across Colorado and is held in collections throughout the United States. Learn more about her work on Instagram @kristenrossart
